   <p>An Extraordinary Moment</p>   <p class="author">by <a href="https://www.npr.org/books/authors/785152934/parker-curry"><span>Parker Curry</span></a>, <a href="https://www.npr.org/books/authors/785152942/jessica-curry"><span>Jessica Curry</span></a> and <a href="https://www.npr.org/books/authors/785152948/brittany-jackson"><span>Brittany Jackson</span></a></p>   <div class="bookinfo">
